Top 100 NES Games
-----------------

Example application in CakePHP that use Afinimaki Recommendations Engine.

Requirements
------------

* Apache web server.
* Mysql database server
* MVC knowledge

CakePHP
-------

This application use official CakePHP package, with follow elements:

* Rate plugin (customized): http://bakery.cakephp.org/articles/view/ajax-star-rating-plugin-1
* Facebook API: http://wiki.developers.facebook.com/index.php/PHP
* AfinimaKi API: 

Installation
------------

1) unpack top100nesgames.(zip/tar.gz) in your webroot
2) restore database with top100nesgames.sql
3) get API key (public and secret) from AfinimaKi
3) create application in Facebook.com. Then get Keys.
4) config database connection in /app/config/database.php
5) config AfinimaKi server connection in /app/controller/games_controller.php

Use
---

1) go http://<your_host>/top100nesgames/
2) click login, then login Facebook Connect
3) rate some items
4) get recommendations
5) enjoy!

Issue
-----

AfinimaKi Recommendations Engine use miles of items to get callifications and 
recommendations. If your applications don't rate nothing, you must insert some 
dummy users and rate more items. You could add more items for get recommendations too.
